'''2-羟氨基乙酸'''（也称'''N-羟基甘氨酸'''）是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为[[C2H5NO3|C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>NO<sub>3</sub>]]。它可由[[2-溴乙酸|2-溴乙酸]]和[[羟胺|羟胺]]在[[乙醇|乙醇]]中于室温反应得到<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Biochemical and Biophysical Research Communications|volume=311|issue=2|language=en|date=2003-11|pages=267–271|doi=10.1016/j.bbrc.2003.09.210|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0006291X03020485|title=3-Alkoxy-5-isoxazolidinones mimic β-lactams|accessdate=2020-06-29|author=Xuefei Cao, Amjad Iqbal, Amit Patel, Paul Gretz, Gregory Huang, Michael Crowder, Richard A Day}}</ref>。它和[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]在[[三乙胺|三乙胺]]的存在下于[[甲醇|甲醇]]中反应，得到N-羧甲基-N-羟基-β-丙氨酸<!-- CAS: 137528-28-0 --><ref>Hayakawa, Hiroshi; Morimoto, Kiyoshi. Preparation of carboxyalkyl-​substituted hydroxylamine derivatives, 1991 JP 03157354 A</ref>。

